extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hello #{ngoName},
  p Congratulations! Your application has been accepted for the project.
  p
    strong Project Details:
  ul
    li
      strong Title: 
      | #{projectTitle}
    li
      strong Description: 
      | #{projectDescription}
    li
      strong Budget: 
      | #{budget} NGN
    li
      strong Location: 
      | #{state}, #{city}
  p Your organization has been selected to implement this project. This is a great opportunity to showcase your expertise and make a meaningful impact in the community.
  p
    strong Next Steps:
  ol
    li Log in to your GivingBack dashboard
    li Review the full project requirements and specifications
    li Prepare your project implementation plan
    li Coordinate with the donor regarding project kickoff
    li Begin project execution according to the agreed timeline
  p You'll be able to track milestones, update progress, and communicate directly with the donor through your dashboard. Make sure to keep the donor informed of any updates or challenges.
  p If you have any questions about the project or need support, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at support@givingback.org.
  p We are excited to support you in delivering excellent results on this project. Let's create positive change together!
  p Thank you for your commitment to our mission and for being a trusted implementation partner.
